<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 21:39:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国的反华声音常常没有切中要害，但在贸易问题上，他们有道理</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3259015/anti-china-voices-us-often-miss-mark-trade-they-have-point?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>拜登对华政策的两名批评者呼吁采取类似于罗纳德·里根对苏联政策的战略。尽管建立了区域联盟，拜登政府却回避与亚洲盟友和伙伴重启自由贸易谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 21:30:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3259015/anti-china-voices-us-often-miss-mark-trade-they-have-point?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官与中国官员举行“坦诚和建设性”会谈</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259103/senior-us-diplomats-hold-frank-and-constructive-talks-chinese-officials?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国国务院表示，丹尼尔·克里滕布林克和莎拉·贝兰正在与中国官员会面，以保持“开放的沟通渠道”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259103/senior-us-diplomats-hold-frank-and-constructive-talks-chinese-officials?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克访问越南，美国科技巨头供应链转移引发中国不安</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259093/apple-ceo-tim-cook-visits-vietnam-us-tech-giants-supply-chain-shift-stirs-unease-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在蒂姆·库克访问期间，苹果表示将增加对东南亚国家供应商的投资。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259093/apple-ceo-tim-cook-visits-vietnam-us-tech-giants-supply-chain-shift-stirs-unease-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国茶饮巨头四川白茶百岛计划在香港进行 2024 年最大的 IPO 融资 3.3 亿美元</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3259090/chinese-tea-shop-giant-sichuan-baicha-baidao-aims-raise-us330-million-hong-kongs-biggest-ipo-2024?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>监管文件显示，中国茶店巨头四川白茶百岛实业计划在香港首次公开募股筹集25亿港元（3.3亿美元），这将是该市今年最大的新股发行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3259090/chinese-tea-shop-giant-sichuan-baicha-baidao-aims-raise-us330-million-hong-kongs-biggest-ipo-2024?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>以色列对中国对伊朗袭击的反应“不如预期强烈”感到“不满”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259101/israel-unhappy-chinas-not-strong-expected-response-iranian-attack?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>驻北京代表团副团长尤瓦尔·瓦克斯表示，该国一直“希望中国外交部予以更严厉的谴责”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:22:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259101/israel-unhappy-chinas-not-strong-expected-response-iranian-attack?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海新建石油钻井平台帮助其深入钻探以保障能源安全</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259084/chinas-new-south-china-sea-oil-rig-helps-it-drill-deep-energy-security?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据报道，新的深海移动作业可以钻探到 9,085 米的深度，这是中国的记录，因为在地缘政治不确定性不断上升的情况下，北京希望减少对进口石油和天然气的依赖。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:01:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259084/chinas-new-south-china-sea-oil-rig-helps-it-drill-deep-energy-security?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在中国，德国的奥拉夫·肖尔茨呼吁“开放和公平”的竞争，因为分歧影响了贸易</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3259063/china-germanys-olaf-scholz-calls-open-and-fair-competition-differences-weigh-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>肖尔茨出访之际，欧盟正在对中国电动汽车进行反补贴调查，而美国对中国产能过剩的批评也越来越多。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3259063/china-germanys-olaf-scholz-calls-open-and-fair-competition-differences-weigh-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>副总理何立峰表示，中国“关键”的房地产行业必须确保房屋及时交付</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259058/chinas-critical-property-sector-must-ensure-timely-delivery-homes-says-vice-premier-he-lifeng?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周末，国务院副总理何立峰结束了对河南省郑州市为期两天的考察，重点关注中国陷入困境的房地产市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259058/chinas-critical-property-sector-must-ensure-timely-delivery-homes-says-vice-premier-he-lifeng?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国在有关“令人震惊”案件的纪录片中透露，它于2016年以间谍罪处决了一名科学家</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259038/china-reveals-it-executed-scientist-spying-2016-documentary-about-shocking-cases?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家电视台播出的节目披露了新的细节，以及对震惊全国的间谍罪的惩罚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259038/china-reveals-it-executed-scientist-spying-2016-documentary-about-shocking-cases?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>全球影响：随着中国反击“永无休止的循环”，中国社交媒体平台 TikTok 在美国面临禁令</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3258993/global-impact-chinese-owned-social-media-platform-tiktok-facing-ban-us-china-hits-back-never-ending?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在本周的《全球影响》时事通讯中，我们关注复杂且不断变化的中美关系，特别关注华盛顿禁止视频分享应用 TikTok 的举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3258993/global-impact-chinese-owned-social-media-platform-tiktok-facing-ban-us-china-hits-back-never-ending?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着制裁迫使莫斯科转向中国，上海是唯一对俄罗斯铝、铜和镍保持开放的大宗商品交易所</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/commodities/article/3259017/shanghai-sole-commodities-bourse-stay-open-russian-aluminium-copper-and-nickel-sanctions-drive?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>对莫斯科实施的能源市场制裁已经对中国的购买习惯产生了巨大影响，帮助俄罗斯去年超越沙特阿拉伯成为北京最大的石油供应国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 05:27:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/commodities/article/3259017/shanghai-sole-commodities-bourse-stay-open-russian-aluminium-copper-and-nickel-sanctions-drive?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>从中国到印度，深度造假如何重塑亚洲政治</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/south-asia/article/3258992/china-india-how-deepfakes-are-reshaping-asian-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>专家表示，随着印度和美国举行重大选举，深度造假技术的兴起可能会对 2024 年的民主构成重大威胁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 02:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/south-asia/article/3258992/china-india-how-deepfakes-are-reshaping-asian-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国急需牛油果，南非已准备好提供出口协议</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258802/china-hungry-avocados-and-south-africa-ready-deliver-export-deal-gets-green-light?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着中国对牛油果的新需求，南非将成为第三个出口牛油果的非洲国家。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 02:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258802/china-hungry-avocados-and-south-africa-ready-deliver-export-deal-gets-green-light?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“平行宇宙”：公关专家詹姆斯·海莫维茨为未来中美关系找到远离政治的希望</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258838/parallel-universes-pr-expert-james-heimowitz-finds-hope-future-us-china-relations-away-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>资深中国观察家表示，恢复民间交流是美中关系更加稳定的关键。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3258838/parallel-universes-pr-expert-james-heimowitz-finds-hope-future-us-china-relations-away-politics?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争